OL,3,CMan Utd fans display 'MUFC proudly
OL,4,Ccolonised by immigrants' banner
OL,6,FManchester United fans displayed a
OL,7,F'MUFC proudly colonised by immigrants'
OL,8,Fbanner at Old Trafford in response to
OL,9,Fa controversial interview given by the
OL,10,Fclub's minority owner Sir Jim
OL,11,FRatcliffe.
OL,13,FRatcliffe was criticised by figures
OL,14,Fincluding Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,15,FStarmer and Mayor of Greater
OL,16,FManchester Andy Burnham after saying
OL,17,Fin an interview with Sky News that the
OL,18,FUK had been "colonised by immigrants"
OL,19,Fwho were "costing too much money".
OL,26,@zD@MOUzD@eO]{D@JOU{D@aO]
