PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772386496
OL,3,CMan Utd fans display 'MUFC proudly
OL,4,Ccolonised by immigrants' banner
OL,6,FMany United fans were upset by the
OL,7,Fcomments from the man who has become
OL,8,Fincreasingly unpopular since buying a
OL,9,Fstake in the club in a deal that was
OL,10,Fagreed at the end of 2023, and some
OL,11,Fmade their feelings known during
OL,12,FSunday's Premier League game at home
OL,13,Fto Crystal Palace.
OL,15,FFans held the banner aloft as players
OL,16,Femerged for the second half at Old
OL,17,FTrafford. It included pictures of
OL,18,Fseveral players, including current
OL,19,Fcaptain Bruno Fernandes, former player
OL,20,Fand manager Ole Gunnar Solksjaer, and
OL,21,FEric Cantona.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1772386496
OL,3,CMan Utd fans display 'MUFC proudly
OL,4,Ccolonised by immigrants' banner
OL,6,FAlso pictured were Park Ji-sung,
OL,7,FPatrice Evra and current players Amad
OL,8,FDiallo and Casemiro.
OL,10,FFollowing his interview Ratcliffe
OL,11,Fissued a statement saying he was sorry
OL,12,Fif his comments had "offended some
OL,13,Fpeople".
OL,15,FThe Football Association reminded
OL,16,FRatcliffe of his responsibilities when
OL,17,Fgiving interviews, but stopped short
OL,18,Fof further sanctions in a decision
OL,19,Fthat was criticised by anti-
OL,20,Fdiscrimination charity Kick It Out.
OL,26,@tD@UOUuD@GO]
